---
title: Umami Miso Bacon and Mushroom Rigatoni with Spinach and Cheese
description: Say hello to miso! Umami is one of the five tastes used when tasting food. A staple in Japanese cuisine, miso is made from fermented soy bean paste and is typical of giving the umami flavour that tastebuds love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W45_UK_QV13339-26_Main_low-87efc866.jpg
